  "description": "<p>Updated for 2020, the new Spark 2.0 now has greater fly coverage and the ability for ultralight fly-and-footprint setup. At, just over a kilo and a half, it's roomy interior gives you plenty of room to hang out, read, escape bugs and, of course, sleep soundly.</p><ul><li>Polyester ripstop fly is UV-resistant and stretches less than nylon when wet</li><li>Lightweight nylon and mesh canopy balance weather protection and ventilation</li><li>Fully seam taped</li><li>DriBase\u2122 waterproof floor offers durable water protection throughout the lifetime of the tent</li><li>Peaked vents in the fly</li><li>Featherlight DAC NSL poles have pressfit connectors and a high strength-to-weight ratio</li><li>Hubbed pole design creates steep walls for greater internal volume</li><li>Reflective zipper pulls and stake-out cords</li><li>2 interior mesh pockets</li><li>Includes 8 DAC aluminum J stakes, guylines and stuff sack</li><li>Optional footprint available for floor protection or an ultralight configuration (sold separately)</li></ul>",
